The paper deals with training a convolutional neural network for image classification tasks in the field of histopathology. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new method for aggregating predictions from smaller regions of the image, which involves machine learning techniques such as quantile function and image augmentation. This suggests that the paper could also belong to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper deals with classification tasks, which could also place it in the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
